教學目標
 



中文
 



本課程以運輸風險管理為主，運輸風險管理程序、策略為輔，並以運輸業風險管理案例進行討論，使學生瞭解運輸風險管理之意義。




英文
 



The objective of the transportation risk management is to provide students to control risk in operations. An efficient transportation risk assessment of hazard identification and safety risk management is essential in controlling risk to acceptable levels. Transportation risk management is centered on an organized approach to hazard identification and risk management with intent to minimize the effect on property, financial, environmental, human and societal losses.




